txt.en: Wanted: Night-touched furs from Azanulbizar to aid the Haban'akkâ of Thráin. Reward to be granted upon delivery.
As promised, you have received a modest reward for delivering the trophies sought by the Haban'akkâ of Thráin.
Haban'akkâ of Thráin Task: Night-touched Furs
The Dwarves of the Haban'akkâ have posted a task to collect night-touched furs at Azanulbizar. These can be turned in for a reward.
Deliver the night-touched furs to a collection box
You have accepted a task to acquire night-touched furs for the Haban'akkâ of Thráin.
Wanted: Night-touched furs from Azanulbizar to aid the Haban'akkâ of Thráin.
